<div class="panel-body list-group collapse out" data-propname="IntroductionAccordion" id="article-IntroductionAccordion" role="tabpanel" style="display: none;">
<p>Measurements of height and weight are key components in evaluating your child's health status. You should be prepared to provide your child’s most current height and weight measurements to their health-care providers at every visit, as these measurements are often used to calculate medication dosages or nutrition needs.</p> </div>
